The following are some canonical keyboard shortcuts for navigating this site:
Keys Action Type C-K Open Search Bar1 Built-In C-S-\ Toggle Light/Dark Custom2 C-S-[ Back One Page Custom C-S-] Next One Page Custom C-S-' To Top Custom C-S-/ To Bottom Custom C-S-, To Site&rsquo;s Home Custom C-S-. To This Page Custom where C-S-Key means Ctrl+Shift+key, C-Key means Ctrl+key.
If you use an extension like vimium or vimium-c, the Esc key might not work as expected when in search mode.&#160;&#x21a9;&#xfe0e;
